# 3. Fungsi untuk membersihkan teks Arab
def clean_arabic(text):
    text = re.sub(r'[\u064B-\u065F]', '', text)  # hapus harakat
    text = re.sub(r'[^\w\s]', '', text)          # hapus tanda baca
    text = re.sub(r'\d+', '', text)              # hapus angka
    return text

cleaned_texts = texts.apply(clean_arabic)

from gensim import corpora, models
import gensim

# Tokenisasi untuk tiap dokumen
tokenized_docs = [word_tokenize(clean_arabic(text)) for text in texts if isinstance(text, str)]

# Hapus stopwords
tokenized_docs = [[word for word in doc if word not in stopwords] for doc in tokenized_docs]

# Buat dictionary dan corpus
dictionary = corpora.Dictionary(tokenized_docs)
corpus = [dictionary.doc2bow(doc) for doc in tokenized_docs]

# Bangun model LDA
lda_model = gensim.models.LdaModel(corpus=corpus,
                                   id2word=dictionary,
                                   num_topics=5,
                                   random_state=42,
                                   passes=10,
                                   per_word_topics=True)

# Tampilkan topik
for idx, topic in lda_model.print_topics(-1):
    print(f"\n Topik {idx+1}:")
    print(topic)

import networkx as nx
from itertools import combinations
from collections import defaultdict
import arabic_reshaper
from bidi.algorithm import get_display


# Bangun co-occurrence matrix
co_occurrence = defaultdict(int)

for doc in tokenized_docs:
    for pair in combinations(set(doc), 2):  # gunakan set agar tidak duplikat dalam satu dokumen
        sorted_pair = tuple(sorted(pair))   # urutkan agar ('a','b') dan ('b','a') sama
        co_occurrence[sorted_pair] += 1

def reshape_arabic(word):
    reshaped = arabic_reshaper.reshape(word)
    return get_display(reshaped)
labels = {node: reshape_arabic(node) for node in G.nodes()}


# Bangun graf
G = nx.Graph()
for (w1, w2), freq in co_occurrence.items():
    if freq > 5:  # tampilkan hanya pasangan yang sering muncul bersama
        G.add_edge(w1, w2, weight=freq)

# Gambar graf
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 12))
pos = nx.spring_layout(G, k=0.5)
nx.draw_networkx_nodes(G, pos, node_color='yellow', node_size=500)
nx.draw_networkx_edges(G, pos, width=1.0, alpha=0.7)
nx.draw_networkx_labels(G, pos, labels=labels, font_family='Arial', font_size=12)
plt.title("Jaringan Kata-Kata yang Sering Muncul Bersamaan dalam Hadis", fontsize=14)
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
plt.savefig("network_graph.png")
